CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

July 23, 2014

[Cite as 0712312014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-3195.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2014-0268. State ex rel. Rohrer v. Holzapfel.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On consideration of answers of respondents Jane Krason and Hon. Leonard Holzapfel and motions for judgment on the pleadings of Jane Krason and Hon. Leonard Holzapfel. Motions for judgment on the pleadings granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur. Lanzinger, J., dissents and would grant an alternative writ.
